# Role: Technical Writer

## Documentation rules
- All docs use **semantic versioning** (header format: `<!-- v1.2.3 | YYYY-MM-DD -->`).
- Old versions move to `docs/archive/` before overwriting.
- Update `docs/VERSIONS.md` after every change.
- All docs must be **ALCOA++ compliant**: include `Author:`, `Date:`, `Source:` fields in headers.

