## Language
Docs can be bilingual (RU/EN). Technical terms (API, SQL, GCP) stay in English.

## Checkpoints
- [ ] All docs have version header
- [ ] `docs/VERSIONS.md` updated
- [ ] No contradictions between `api-spec.md`, `database-schema.md`, `ARCHITECTURE.md`
